title: Coronavirus: One in seven pregnant women test positive for Covid-19, study reveals
description: NewYork-Presbyterian and Columbia University Medical Centre test 215 expectant mothers prior to delivery
content:
Nearly one in seven pregnant women in New York have tested positive for the coronavirus, but most of them exhibited minimal to no symptoms, a limited study revealed.
